For this assignment you are going to explore the chord object. Create your own chord progression, using either the addChord or setChord methods. Then explore:
* how to use the get method to play chords
* how to use the arp method to play arpeggios
* what changing the min and max properties does
* what changing the length does
* what changing the voicing does (for the arpeggiator)
